  <h1>Introduction to MERN stack</h1>

  <p>
    The MERN stack is a popular set of technologies used for building full-stack JavaScript applications. 
    It combines MongoDB, Express.js, React, and Node.js to enable efficient development of modern web applications. 
  </p>

  <ol>
    <li>MongoDB</li>
    <li>Express.js</li>
    <li>React</li>
    <li>Node.js</li>
